pageProduct.description:
General Information

Probiotic love bugs for digestive health.

TRUST YOUR GUT
A healthy digestive system (a.k.a. gut) essentially helps run the show when it comes to your overall general health. In fact, your gut houses approximately 70% of the cells that help make up your immune system. That's why we believe nourishing your gut with good bacteria is so important. 

WHY CHEW SUP?
Chew your supplements with SUP's delish gummies.SUP nourishes your digestive system with probiotics for: 
-Digestive wellness
-Growth of good gut bacteria
-Inner wellbeing
-1 Billion CFU per serve CHEWSUP

Size: 65 Gummies

KEY FEATURES

• Digestive wellness
• Growth of good gut bacteria
• Inner wellbeing
• 1 Billion CFU per serve
• 99% Sugar Free

Warnings

Excess consumption of the product may have a laxative effect. MAY CONTAIN WHEAT. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing. Reseal immediately after use.

Ingredients

Sweetener (maltitol), Water, Gelling agent (gelatine),Bulking agent (maize starch), Acidity regulator (331, 330), Natural flavour, Bacillus coagulans (0.6%), Colour (163), Glazing agent (coconut oil, beeswax, carnauba wax).

Contains: MAY CONTAIN WHEAT

Allergen May Be Present: Wheat

Directions

Take 2 Gummies per day

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
